title: Gold 4 looking for ranked teams
body:
Game Name: 0oAlkalineo0
Usually available at night after 6pm and available on weekends after 1pm (Auckland time)
Ranked status: G4
Roles: I main sup, sometimes go mid if someone else wants sup. Sup > Mid > Jg > ADC (NO TOP)
Summary: I am good with sup and mid, jungle depends on what champ I play, not that great with cs when I adc and suck playing top.
Please add me in game if you want me to join your team =)

replies.body: I have people adding me in game but did not add me onto their ranked team. I am looking for committed teams so please only add me if you sincerely want someone to join. Thanks
